merchant.name: Urban Mix - One Raffles Place
merchant.description: Urban Mix offers affordable and flavour-packed food inspired by cuisines from around the world. Urban Mix offers healthy, fresh, and flavorful menu items that customers can customize to their own liking. The combinations are nearly endless. Healthy doesn't mean boring! Create your own Urban Mix to eat better and feel better.

items.name: Build Your Own Mix
items.description: 1 Base, 1 Protein, 2 Side Salads, 3 Toppings, 1 Sauce

items.name: Gangnam Style
items.description: Thinly sliced pork belly, chargrilled chicken thigh, sauteed onions, kimchi, sesame seeds, shredded cabbage, carrots over kimchi fried rice with Korean ssamjang sauce

items.name: UMazing Surf N' Turf
items.description: Grilled prawn, roast beef, baked potatoes, sauteed onions, sweet corn with smoky bbq sauce over garlic rice

items.name: Viva Mexico
items.description: Bbq pulled pork, bell peppers, sauteed onions, guacamole, pico de gallo, shredded cheese, nacho chips, jalapenos, and Vatos hot sauce over mexican rice

items.name: L.A. Crossfit
items.description: Romaine lettuce, chicken breast, hummus, mushrooms, broccoli, cherry tomatoes, chick peas, shredded cabbage, sweet corn, egg with roasted sesame dressing.

items.name: Little Tokyo
items.description: Chargrilled chicken thigh, crab mayo salad, garlic edamame, sauteed onions, furikake, shredded cabbage, sweet corn, soy sesame dressing over cha soba (green tea soba) noodles

items.name: Gluten Free Guilt Free
items.description: Baby spinach, chicken breast, mushrooms, broccoli, avocado, sweet corn, hard boiled egg, shredded cabbage, shredded carrots, with honey mustard sauce
